title: Wolfman Jack's One Hit Wonders (Big Papi)
description:
Source:  CD + Fresh Cover Art Scan

The first track has Wolfman Jack doing his DJ thing but it seems random and spliced before the song Brandy like it doesn't belong.  Heating his voice is very cool but they good have paid better hommage than that...just thoughts.  

For those of you who did not get the memo, Wolfman Jack is a famous American radio disc jockey.  The first of his kind.  He was also the DJ in American Graffiti and he passed away in 1995.

- Big Papi
